data.description: Move in Ready, 3 bedroom, 2 bath home located in the highly sought out community of Bella Vita. This house is located on a cul-de-sac lot and has great curb appeal, including a low maintenance flower bed with river rock. When you step inside, you will walk through the large foyer and taken back by the open concept floor plan with vaulted ceilings, and plenty of natural light pouring in through an abundance of windows. The kitchen is a chef's dream, including staggered white cabinets with crown, granite counters, stainless steel Whirlpool appliances including a GAS range, work island, breakfast bar, single basin under-mount sink, large pantry, and a spacious Carolina Room. There is also a formal dining area with elegant wainscot molding. Also featured in this home is a split bedroom plan, allowing for plenty of privacy for your guests. The primary suite boasts a vast walk-in closet, sitting area, bay window, garden tub, separate shower and double sinks. The laundry room also has plenty of space, and includes a built-in storage bench and cabinets. Outside, you will find a patio, and plenty of space on this sizable yard to entertain family and friends. The community of Bella Vita features a community pool, clubhouse and fitness center and conveniently located near plenty of shopping, dining, entertainment, golf courses- and just a short drive to the beach. Square footage is approximate and not guaranteed. Buyer responsible for verification.
